title: Georges Seurat A Sunday on La Grande Jatte—1884 Tote
description:
Tote developed from Georges Seurat’s A Sunday on La Grande Jatte—1884, 1884-86, from the Art Institute of Chicago’s collection

This tote is perfect for a any occasion, and provides the opportunity to look at the details of this wonderful painting as you carry it with you.

  • Dimensions: 16.5 x 12 in.
  • Material: Polyester.
  • Zipper closure.
